{
  "stem": "24171.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just didn't know exactly about the thing, but that's what it was, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no place, kind of, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- [? things. ?] And so when we came there to the school, and it was Friday afternoon and then everybody got back, and we, oh, got a big pot with soup and chicken in it to carry with one side and the other side, and we left it there by the school because everything has to go in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In a hurry, they start to put us already at that time like five in a row.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't do that there, because that was a stony place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so but we came down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It took about five minutes to come down to the main road, and then there on the main road they-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] so we went and walked to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In [INAUDIBLE], they put us in the shul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like an hour and a half to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Men, women, and children with the gendarmes by the side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody behaved and everybody-- people were crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Going why, what's going on, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't-- I don't know if somebody dared to ask the gendarme.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I really don't know but whoever I seen in the front, you know, for me, I could see them now there in the road.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was nice, it was not rainy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a nice weather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to [INAUDIBLE], and they put us in the shul.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there was already from another village in the shul.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Other people from Barry's, from my husband's village, they were already somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
